    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you ready to fall in love with your next ride? I\u2019m selling my absolute pride and joy, and let me tell you\u2014she is a total showstopper! This car is in truly flawless condition and has been babied since day one. It's been kept tucked away in a garage, and honestly, it still looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor. Not a single scratch or dent to be found, and the interior is absolutely spotless! It drives like a dream and looks even better in person. I'm sad to see it go, but I know the next owner is going to be over the moon. Come check it out and see for yourself!",
      "price": 44900.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
