    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "This 2019 Porsche Cayman is a true collector-grade specimen, meticulously maintained and presented in showroom condition. The Guards Red exterior retains a deep, mirror-like luster thanks to a professional ceramic coating and a lifetime of climate-controlled garage storage. There are absolutely no rock chips, swirl marks, or imperfections to be found on the bodywork. Inside, the black leather interior is indistinguishable from new; the seat bolsters show zero wear, the dashboard is pristine, and the cabin still carries that signature new-car scent. Mechanically, the car is flawless. It comes with a full, documented service history from authorized dealerships, including a recent major service and a fresh set of Michelin Pilot Sport 4S tires. Every button, switch, and feature operates exactly as it did the day it rolled off the assembly line. This is an uncompromising vehicle for the buyer who demands the absolute best. Includes all original manuals, two keys, and a custom car cover.",
