    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This 981-generation Cayman S is a superlative example of mid-engine precision. Powered by a naturally aspirated 3.4L boxer-six featuring VarioCam Plus and DFI, it delivers linear power delivery through a crisp 6-speed manual transaxle. The chassis is equipped with PASM (Porsche Active Suspension Management) and PTV (Porsche Torque Vectoring), ensuring optimal lateral grip and turn-in response. Meticulously maintained with a documented service history, this vehicle retains its factory-fresh structural integrity and cosmetic luster. The undercarriage is pristine, and the interior exhibits zero bolster fatigue or switchgear wear. A true turn-key investment for the discerning driver seeking the pinnacle of analog engagement.",
